law.text:
As used in 212.810 to 212.930, unless the content requires otherwise:
"Cabinet" means the Cabinet for Health and Family Services; and
"Health officer" means the chief administrative officer of the district health department.
law.history: Amended 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 99, sec. 423, effective June 20, 2005. -- Amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 426, sec. 374, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. VI, sec. 107(1) and (11). -- Created 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 301, sec. 3.
